  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join our Discord  Or ELSE!....Or else you'll miss out on updates, competitions and having a big impact on this project... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1459070/extras/7605000bb84bfe4efe8dcffbfc5c4941.poster.avif?t=1734125672\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1459070/extras/7605000bb84bfe4efe8dcffbfc5c4941.webm?t=1734125672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1459070/extras/7605000bb84bfe4efe8dcffbfc5c4941.mp4?t=1734125672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FADE</strong> is an <strong>Dark Fantasy Action RPG</strong> that combines combat inspired by the <strong>“Souls Series”</strong> with the narrative direction of <strong>FABLE</strong> and the anime <strong>Full Metal Alchemist</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1459070/extras/cdca02438938cb4bb677b05e05425258.poster.avif?t=1734125672\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1459070/extras/cdca02438938cb4bb677b05e05425258.webm?t=1734125672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1459070/extras/cdca02438938cb4bb677b05e05425258.mp4?t=1734125672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>FADE</strong> players will be tasked with exploring the settlements of <strong>Celeste, Solemn, Whisper, and The Baltane Capital</strong> in order stop the <strong>5 Homunculus Monarchs</strong>, each with their own unique spin on alchemy and combat, sharing a destructive plot to sacrifice the country.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To succeed in your journey you'll have to, take on side quests, craft useful items and collect powerful equipment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1459070/extras/a74edffe5de41e4168c92b00d4fb7fe7.avif?t=1734125672\" width=601 height=165 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join our Discord  Or ELSE!....Or else you'll miss out on updates, competitions and having a big impact on this project... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1459070/extras/7605000bb84bfe4efe8dcffbfc5c4941.poster.avif?t=1734125672\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1459070/extras/7605000bb84bfe4efe8dcffbfc5c4941.webm?t=1734125672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1459070/extras/7605000bb84bfe4efe8dcffbfc5c4941.mp4?t=1734125672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FADE</strong> is an <strong>Dark Fantasy Action RPG</strong> that combines combat inspired by the <strong>“Souls Series”</strong> with the narrative direction of <strong>FABLE</strong> and the anime <strong>Full Metal Alchemist</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1459070/extras/cdca02438938cb4bb677b05e05425258.poster.avif?t=1734125672\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1459070/extras/cdca02438938cb4bb677b05e05425258.webm?t=1734125672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1459070/extras/cdca02438938cb4bb677b05e05425258.mp4?t=1734125672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>FADE</strong> players will be tasked with exploring the settlements of <strong>Celeste, Solemn, Whisper, and The Baltane Capital</strong> in order stop the <strong>5 Homunculus Monarchs</strong>, each with their own unique spin on alchemy and combat, sharing a destructive plot to sacrifice the country.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To succeed in your journey you'll have to, take on side quests, craft useful items and collect powerful equipment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1459070/extras/a74edffe5de41e4168c92b00d4fb7fe7.avif?t=1734125672\" width=601 height=165 /></span></p>",
